<br>
Everyone showing up at the raid should have 50pp to cover reagents and consumables used during the raid.<br>
<br>
Some people may ask, &quot;Why 50pp?&quot;.  Well, here's a brief answer:<br>
<br>
The 50pp is used to cover the reagents we use during buffing.  Now, while the reagents we use may not total 50pp per person for some raids, this fee is also used to help fund future raids and other events.  Some times we come up a little short, some times we come up ahead... and things generally seem to balance out across all the raids CoG hosts. <p>-Kommisar Nils "Can-Head" Hansen -- Guild Officer. Master Smith. Tank.
